{"arkId":"cl010094295","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010094295","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Saint-Jacques le majeur","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Saint-Jacques le majeur"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1715","currentLocation":"Denon, [SCULPT] Salle 403 - Galerie Michel-Ange, Vitrine 17","room":"Salle 403, Aile Aile Denon, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":"","endYear":1715,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Rusconi, Camillo","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1658","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1728","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q2706478"},{"label":"Italie","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 2448","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statuette","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0,68","displayDimension":"0,68 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,42","displayDimension":"0,42 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,4","displayDimension":"0,4 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"terre cuite","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Probablement un des deux petits mod\u00e8les, ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s en 1715, pour la statue colossale en marbre plac\u00e9e en 1718 dans une niche de la basilique Saint-Jean-de-Latran \u00e0 Rome. Collection Marcel Boulanger\u00a0; sa vente, Paris, le 13\u00a0d\u00e9cembre 1929, n\u00b0 207 (attribu\u00e9 \u00e0 Caffieri, comme \u00ab\u00a0Christ marchant et contemplant\u00a0\u00bb). Don de l\u2019antiquaire Paul-Georges\u00a0Gouvert (Paris, 1880 - Paris, 1959), 1936.\r\nLa statuette a \u00e9t\u00e9 bris\u00e9e en plusieurs endroits. Une intervention ancienne a modifi\u00e9 le geste de l\u0027avant-bras droit qui, \u00e0 l\u0027origine, \u00e9tait nu et tenait \u00e0 la verticale le b\u00e2ton de p\u00e8lerin : le bras fut recouvert d\u0027une manche et la main remodel\u00e9e avec l\u0027index tendu, transformant le saint en Christ pr\u00eachant ; le revers, originellement \u00e9vid\u00e9, fut renforc\u00e9 par des goujons et combl\u00e9 en pl\u00e2tre. La restauration r\u00e9cente a partiellement d\u00e9gag\u00e9 l\u0027avant-bras nu, et laiss\u00e9 au revers une partie du renfort en pl\u00e2tre.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Boulanger, Marcel","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"M. Gouvert, Paul Georges","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1936","startYear":1936,"endYear":1936}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"material":[{"value":"terre cuite"}],"objectType":[{"value":"statuette"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Di Macco, Michela ; Dardanello, Giuseppe ; Gauna, Chiara (dir.), Sfida al Barocco. 1680-1750. Roma, Torino, Parigi, cat. exp. (Turin (Italie), La Venaria Reale, Citroniera